      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in a car that\u2019s got character and plenty of life left! This vehicle is in fair condition, showing some honest signs of its journey but still offering a dependable and steady ride for its next owner. It\u2019s a fantastic choice for someone looking for a solid, functional vehicle at a great value\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend errands!",
