    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as a reliable but aged daily driver. The engine and transmission are currently functional, though the engine shows some minor oil seepage and the gear shifts are not as crisp as they once were. Externally, the paint has some fading and several noticeable scratches and small dings. The interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and some of the plastic trim is cracked. It is a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and potential upcoming maintenance needs.",
