      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a solid, smooth experience on the road. It\u2019s got a little bit of character from being enjoyed, but it\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready to hit the pavement with a new owner! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
