      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior paint retains a beautiful gloss, though there are minor surface scratches and a few small stone chips on the hood consistent with highway miles. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has never been smoked in; the upholstery is free of tears, showing only slight wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All electronics, including the infotainment system and climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is solid, with a comprehensive service history and a recently completed oil change and brake inspection. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts crisply, and the tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining. It is a dependable, honest car that has been cared for and is ready for the road.",
